  <h3>WHY TREES:</h3>
  <div class="whytrees">
    Trees are of invaluable importance to our environment and
    human well-being. They give us air to breathe, clean water to
    drink, shade, and food to humans, animals and plants. They
    provide habitats for numerous species of fauna and flora.
