    <ol>
      <li>Plant a Tree where you can.</li>
      <li>Go paperless at home and in the office.</li>
      <li>Buy recycled products and then recycle them again.</li>
      <li>Buy certified wood products. Read the labels and look for the FSC
        (Forest Stewardship Council) mark.</li>
      <li>Your power as a consumer is vital to stopping deforestation. Just like
        any business, if theres no demand then the supply will be lessened.</li>
    </ol>

